14:03.680 --> 14:06.180
(horn honking)

14:06.180 --> 14:07.680
Okay, okay,
they're waiting for us.

14:07.680 --> 14:09.380
Now, are you going to come--
yes or no?

14:09.380 --> 14:11.350
I can't.
Let's go, Pots.

14:11.350 --> 14:12.350
I can't figure him out.

14:12.350 --> 14:13.350
Yeah.

14:13.350 --> 14:14.850
What are we going to
do with Miss Trout?

14:14.850 --> 14:17.860
I don't know,
she's too good to throw back.

14:18.810 --> 14:20.890
(door closes)

14:20.890 --> 14:22.900
Miss Trout.

14:22.900 --> 14:27.400
Boy, would I like
to swim upstream with her.

14:27.400 --> 14:29.030
That Fonzie.

14:29.030 --> 14:32.120
